description: Beneath a sturdy white cedar ceiling, a snarling war griffin painting hangs on one of the patterned white walls.  A gold-trimmed ebonwood chest and a wide faenor-trimmed table sit in opposite corners while an ivory elven noble statue rests on a polished marble floor.
